page.title: 11FISHING
page.content: MARK , MICHAEL AND I WENT FISHING AT CARLTON LODGE IN CARLTON MINIOTT.WE WENT AT 9.30 AM.WE TOOK WITH US A FISHING ROD AND MAGGOTS EACH.A MAN CAME TO US AND ASKED FOR 50 PENCE AND GAVE US A TICKET.WE GOT OUR FISHING RODS OUT OF THE CASES AND STARTED TO FISH.AT FIRST WE GOT OUR FLOATS STUCK UP IN THE TREE.EVENTUALLY WE GOT OUR FISHING LINES IN THE WATER.SOON MARK FELT A BITE BUT IT WAS A LOAD OF WEEDS.WE PUT LOTS OF MAGGOTS ON OUR HOOKS.IN A FEW MINUTES MICHAEL NEARLY CAUGHT A PIKE.THE PIKE JUMPED OUT OF THE WATER FOR THE MAGGOTS.AFTER OUR PACKED LUNCH WE MOVED TO A DIFFERENT PLACE.WE DIDN'T CATCH ANYTHING SO WE PACKED UP AND WENT HOME.
